    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014it is a total dream! This car is in truly stunning condition; I\u2019ve kept it tucked away in the garage and pampered it since day one. It looks and drives like it's brand new, with not a single blemish to be found. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been loved and maintained to perfection, this is the one for you! Feel free to drop me a message if you want to come by and see it for yourself!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
