      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty in person to believe it\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car, and it\u2019s in truly pristine, mint condition without a single worry to be found. It drives like a dream and looks even better. I'm looking for a great new home for it, so come take a look and let's get you on the road in style!",
